      "value": "<p><strong>Category</strong>: Clan <br /><strong>Prerequisite</strong>: Kamizuru Clan <br />You've adopted the way your insects harness chakra, you gain the following benefits;</p><ul><li>Increase your Wisdom score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li><li>You may use your Wisdom instead of Intelligence as your Ninjutsu ability modifier when casting Kamizuru Clan Hijutsu.</li><li>You learn one additional Kamizuru Hijutsu that you qualify for.</li><li>You can learn and create Kamizuru Hijutsu in half the time.</li><li><p>You gain resistance to Poison Damage.</p></li></ul>",
